OL,5, A German ballet choreographer who      
OL,6, smeared dog faeces on the face of a    
OL,7, newspaper critic has been sacked.      
OL,9,FMarco Goecke was the ballet director at
OL,10,Fthe Hanover State Opera when he        
OL,11,Fconfronted a journalist for writing a  
OL,12,Fbad review about one of his shows.     
OL,14,FThe opera house has now fired him,     
OL,15,Fsaying his "irresponsible actions have 
OL,16,Fdeeply unsettled the audience" and     
OL,17,F"irritated the public".                
OL,19,FHe had "massively damaged" the opera   
OL,20,Fhouse's reputation, it added.          
